
<input type="hidden" name="user" value="{{user.id}}">
<div class="main-container profile">
    <h1 style="font-size:20px; font-weight:700;" class="my-5">Mis datos</h1>
{{!--account data--}}
    <div class="section d-flex mb-3">
        <div class="section__title" style="width:60%; line-height:1.25;">
            <h2 class="subtitle "style="font-size:18px; font-weight:700;">Datos de la cuenta</h2>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="andes-card andes-card--flat andes-card--default profile-card andes-card--padding-default">
        <div class="row__value">
            <div class="col-sm my-3">
            Usuario
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3">
            {{user.username}}
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3 text-right">
                <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 6 10" class="right-arrow">
                    <path fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke="#3483FA" stroke-width="1.5" d="M1 1l4 4-4 4"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
       
        <div class="row__value">
            <div class="col-sm my-3">
            Email
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3">
            {{user.email}}
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3 text-right">
                <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 6 10" class="right-arrow">
                    <path fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke="#3483FA" stroke-width="1.5" d="M1 1l4 4-4 4"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{{!-- personal data --}}
<div class="section d-flex mb-3">
        <div class="section__title" style="width:60%; line-height:1.25;">
            <h2 class="subtitle "style="font-size:18px; font-weight:700;">Datos personales</h2>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="andes-card andes-card--flat andes-card--default profile-card andes-card--padding-default">
        <div class="row__value">
            <div class="col-sm my-3">Nombre y apellido</div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3">{{user.name}} {{user.lastname}}</div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3 text-right">
                <a tabindex="0"  role="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalPoll-1" title="Dismissible popover"
                data-content="And here's some amazing content. It's very engaging. Right?">
                <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 6 10" class="right-arrow">
                    <path fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke="#3483FA" stroke-width="1.5" d="M1 1l4 4-4 4"></path>
                </svg>
                </a>
                <!-- Modal: modalPoll -->
                <div class="modal fade right" id="modalPoll-1" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
                    aria-hidden="true" data-backdrop="false">
                    <div class="modal-dialog modal-full-height modal-right modal-notify modal-info" role="document">
                        <div class="modal-content">
                        <!--Header-->
                        <div class="modal-header">
                            <p class="heading lead">Corregir mi nombre y/o apellido</p>
                            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                            <span aria-hidden="true" class="white-text">×</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <!--Body-->
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <div class="text-center">
                            <i class="far fa-file-alt fa-4x mb-3 animated rotateIn"></i>                                               
                            </div>

                            <hr>                                                
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="text-left">
                               Si es por un error ortográfico en tu nombre o apellido, o si te registraste con tu DNI verdadero y un nombre de fantasía, y querés cambiarlo al real, <a href="#"> podés corregirlo</a>. Vas a necesitar fotos del frente y del dorso de tu DNI para validar el cambio.
                                </div>



                                <div class="text-left mt-5" >
                                   Si lo que querés es tener tu cuenta a nombre de otra persona o empresa, entonces tenés que <a href="#"> cambiar la titularidad de tu cuenta</a>.
                                </div>
                            </div>                        

                        </div>

                        <!--Footer-->
                        <div class="modal-footer justify-content-center">                        
                            <a type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary waves-effect" data-dismiss="modal">Cerrar</a>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Modal: modalPoll -->
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row__value">
            <div class="col-sm my-3">Documento</div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3">{{user.dni}}</div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3 text-right">
                <a tabindex="0"  role="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalPoll-2" title="Dismissible popover"
                data-content="And here's some amazing content. It's very engaging. Right?">
                <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 6 10" class="right-arrow">
                    <path fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke="#3483FA" stroke-width="1.5" d="M1 1l4 4-4 4"></path>
                </svg>
                </a>                
                               
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row__value">
            <div class="col-sm my-3">Teléfono</div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3" id="userTel">{{user.telephone}}</div>
            <div class="col-sm my-3 pr-0">
